This may occur if you are calling 'Dispose' on the context instance, or wrapping it in a using statement. If you are using dependency injection, you should let the dependency injection container take care of disposing context instances.

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[AddressId], [s].[CreatedAt], [s].[CreatedById], [s].[DeletedById], [s].[DeleteteAt], [s].[Dob], [s].[FirstName], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[LastName], [s].[UpdatedAt], [s].[UpdatedById], [s].[UserID], [t].[CoursesId], [t].[StudentsId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[CreatedById], [t].[DeletedById], [t].[DeleteteAt], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[Level], [t].[Name], [t].[ShortDescription], [t].[UpdatedAt], [t].[UpdatedById], [t].[UserID]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[CoursesId], [c].[StudentsId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreatedAt], [c0].[CreatedById], [c0].[DeletedById], [c0].[DeleteteAt], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[Level], [c0].[Name], [c0].[ShortDescription], [c0].[UpdatedAt], [c0].[UpdatedById], [c0].[UserID]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[StudentsId]
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], [s].[Id], [t].[CoursesId], [t].[StudentsId]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[AddressId], [s].[CreatedAt], [s].[CreatedById], [s].[DeletedById], [s].[DeleteteAt], [s].[Dob], [s].[FirstName], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[LastName], [s].[UpdatedAt], [s].[UpdatedById], [s].[UserID], [t].[CoursesId], [t].[StudentsId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[CreatedById], [t].[DeletedById], [t].[DeleteteAt], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[Level], [t].[Name], [t].[ShortDescription], [t].[UpdatedAt], [t].[UpdatedById], [t].[UserID]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[CoursesId], [c].[StudentsId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreatedAt], [c0].[CreatedById], [c0].[DeletedById], [c0].[DeleteteAt], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[Level], [c0].[Name], [c0].[ShortDescription], [c0].[UpdatedAt], [c0].[UpdatedById], [c0].[UserID]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[StudentsId]
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], [s].[Id], [t].[CoursesId], [t].[StudentsId]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]

        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (

    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Addresses] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Addresses] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Addresses] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Addresses] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]

2022-06-01 22:25:32.577 -07:00 [ERR] Failed executing DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Addresses] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName], DATEPART(year, [s].[Dob]) - DATEPART(year, GETDATE()) AS [Age], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CoursesId] = [c2].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c1].[StudentsId]) AS [CourseName], [a].[Street], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode], [a].[Country], [a].[Comunity], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c4].[Name]
    FROM [CategoryCourse] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c4] ON [c3].[CategoriesId] = [c4].[Id]
    WHERE ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c6].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CoursesId] = [c6].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c5].[StudentsId]) IS NOT NULL) AND ((
        SELECT TOP(1) [c8].[Id]
        FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c7]
        INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CoursesId] = [c8].[Id]
        WHERE [s].[Id] = [c7].[StudentsId]) = [c3].[CoursesId])) AS [Category]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Addresses] AS [a] ON [s].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseStudent] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Courses] AS [c0] ON [c].[CoursesId] = [c0].[Id]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudentsId]) > 0
ORDER BY [s].[FirstName], [s].[LastName]
